beginning. Containing an area of ONE HUNDRED THREE THOUSAND SEVEN HUNDRED FOUR (103,704) SQUARE METERS, more or less subject for precise survey.

The Philippine Reclamation Authority (PRA) shall pay the value of the land to the National Government through the Department of Environment and Natural Resources (DENR) which shall conduct the appraisal of the land.

The Secretary of the Department of Environment and Natural Resources is hereby authorized to issue the corresponding Special Patent in favor of PRA upon full payment of the total value of the land.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 23 rd day of October, in the year of Our Lord Two Thousand and Nine.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President:

Executive Secretary
